{"kanda":6,"sarga":2,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"तंतुशोकपरिद्यूनंरामंदशरथात्मजम् ।उवाचवचनंश्रीमान् सुग्रीवश्शोकनाशनम्","trans":"Glorious Sugriva spoke such words of advice to remove the agony of Rama,son of Dasaratha, who was filled with sorrow.","words":[{"d":"श्रीमान्:","m":"glorious"},{"d":"सुग्रीवः","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"शोकपरिद्यूनम्:","m":"one who is filled with sorrow"},{"d":"दशरथात्मजम्:","m":"Dasaratha's son"},{"d":"तम्:","m":"him"},{"d":"रामम्:","m":"at Rama"},{"d":"शोकनाशनम्:","m":"to remove the agony"},{"d":"वचनम्:","m":"words of advice"},{"d":"उवाच:","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"किंत्वंसन्तप्यसेवीर यथान्यःप्राकृतस्तथा ।मैवंभूस्त्यजसन्तापंकृतघ्नइवसौहृदम्","trans":"\"Heroic Rama Why are you grieving like a common man? Give up your grief just like an ungrateful one gives up friendship.\"","words":[{"d":"वीर:","m":"heroic"},{"d":"अन्यः","m":"like others"},{"d":"प्राकृतः","m":"common man"},{"d":"यथा:","m":"likewise"},{"d":"तथा:","m":"that way"},{"d":"त्वया:","m":"by you"},{"d":"किम्:","m":"why"},{"d":"तप्यते:","m":"give up grief"},{"d":"एवम्:","m":"that way"},{"d":"माभूः","m":"do not be"},{"d":"एवम:","m":"like this"},{"d":"कृतघ्नः","m":"ungrateful one"},{"d":"इव:","m":"like that"},{"d":"सन्तापम्:","m":"grief"},{"d":"त्यज:","m":"give up सौहृदम्: friendship"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"सन्तापस्यचतेस्थानंनहिपश्यामिराघव ।प्रवृत्तावुपलब्धायांज्ञातेचनिलयेरिपोः","trans":"\"Raghava Having secured the information (of Sita) and known the location of the enemy's residence, I do not see the reason for your mourning.\"","words":[{"d":"राघव:","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"प्रवृत्तौ:","m":"information"},{"d":"उपलब्धायाम्:","m":"having secured,ज्ञाते: knowing"},{"d":"चनिलयेरिपोः","m":"and the enemy's residence"},{"d":"सन्तापस्य:","m":"mourning"},{"d":"स्थानम्:","m":"location"},{"d":"नपश्यामिहि:","m":"I do not see the reason"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"मतिमान्शास्त्रवित्प्राज्ञःपण्डितश्चासिराघव ।त्यजेमांपापिकांबुद्धिंकृतात्मेवार्थदूषणीम्","trans":"\"Raghava You are an intellectual, well versed in Sastras, wise and learned. Give up this sinful thought just as the one who is efficient gives up the one who violates subtle truth.\"","words":[{"d":"राघव:","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"मतिमान्:","m":"an intellectual"},{"d":"शास्त्रवित्:","m":"one who is well versed in Sastras"},{"d":"प्राज्ञः","m":"one who is wise"},{"d":"पण्डितश्चअसि:","m":"and who is learned also"},{"d":"कृतात्मा:","m":"one who is efficient"},{"d":"अर्थदूषणीम्:","m":"one who is a violator of subtle truth"},{"d":"बुद्धिम्:","m":"intellect"},{"d":"इमाम्:","m":"these"},{"d":"पापिकाम्:","m":"sinful"},{"d":"त्यज:","m":"give up"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"समुद्रंलङ्घयित्वातुमहानक्रसमाकुलम् ।लङ्कामारोहयिष्यामोहनिष्यामश्चतेरिपुम्","trans":"\"If we cross over that ocean infested with huge crocodiles and ascend the fortress of Lanka, know that the enemy is killed.\"","words":[{"d":"महानक्रसमाकुलम्:","m":"that which is infested with huge crocodiles"},{"d":"समुद्रम्:","m":"ocean"},{"d":"लङ्घयित्वा:","m":"if we cross over"},{"d":"लङ्काम्:","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"आरोहयिष्याम:","m":"ascending the fortress"},{"d":"ते:","m":"your"},{"d":"रिपुम्:","m":"enemy"},{"d":"हनिष्यामश्च:","m":"know that he is killed"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"निरुत्साहस्यदीनस्यशोकपर्याकुलात्मनः ।सर्वार्थाव्यवसीदन्तिव्यसनंचाधिगच्छति","trans":"\"One who is despondent, dejected and overwhelmed with grief, will be dispirited in all matters. Not only that with worry he will meet with disaster.\"","words":[{"d":"निरुत्साहस्य:","m":"one who is despondent"},{"d":"दीनस्य:","m":"for a dejected person"},{"d":"शोकपर्याकुलात्मनः","m":"overwhelmed with grief"},{"d":"सर्वार्थाः","m":"in all matters"},{"d":"व्यवसीदन्ति:","m":"dispirited"},{"d":"व्यसनंच:","m":"and worry"},{"d":"अधिगच्छति:","m":"will be destroyed"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"इमेशूरास्समर्थाश्चसर्वनोहरियूथपाः ।त्वत्प्रियार्थंकृतोत्साहाःप्रवेष्टुमपिपावकम् ।एषांहर्षेणजानामितर्कश्चास्मिन् दृढोमम","trans":"All these vanara leaders and heroes are highly capable and for your happiness they are even ready to enter fire. I know this from their joy and I even infer that it is certain (to happen).","words":[{"d":"सर्वतः","m":"all these"},{"d":"इमे:","m":"to you"},{"d":"हरियूथपाः","m":"vanara leaders"},{"d":"शूराः","m":"heroes"},{"d":"समर्थाश्च:","m":"highly capable"},{"d":"त्वत्प्रियार्थम् :","m":"for your happiness"},{"d":"पावकम्:","m":"fire"},{"d":"प्रवेष्टुम्:","m":"to enter अपि: also"},{"d":"कृतोत्साहः","m":"are ready"},{"d":"एषाम्:","m":"these"},{"d":"हर्षेण:","m":"joy"},{"d":"जानामि:","m":"I know"},{"d":"मम:","m":"me"},{"d":"तर्कश्चापि:","m":"even infer"},{"d":"दृढः","m":"I am certain"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"विक्रमेणसमानेष्येसीतांहत्वायथारिपुम् ।रावणंपापकर्माणंतथात्वंकर्तुमर्हसि","trans":"\"You ought to work such that we would kill that enemy Ravana of sinful deeds with our prowess and get back Sita. I hope you are capable of doing that.\"","words":[{"d":"रिपुम्:","m":"enemy"},{"d":"पापकर्माणम्:","m":"one of sinful deeds"},{"d":"रावणम्:","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"विक्रमेण:","m":"with  prowess"},{"d":"हत्वा:","m":"on killing"},{"d":"सीताम्:","m":"Sita"},{"d":"यथा:","m":"that way"},{"d":"समानेष्ये:","m":"bring back"},{"d":"तथा:","m":"that way"},{"d":"त्वम्:","m":"your"},{"d":"कर्तुम्:","m":"will do"},{"d":"अर्हसि:","m":"you ought to"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"सेतुरत्रयथाबध्येद्यथापश्येमतांपुरीम् ।तस्यराक्षसराजस्यतथात्वंकुरुराघव","trans":"\"Raghava You think that we will be building a bridge and then seeing that city of the king of Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"राघव:","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"अत्र:","m":"there"},{"d":"सेतुः","m":"bridge"},{"d":"यथा:","m":"in that way"},{"d":"बध्येत्:","m":"would build"},{"d":"तस्य:","m":"his"},{"d":"राक्षसराजस्य:","m":"rakshasa king's"},{"d":"ताम्:","m":"that"},{"d":"पुरीम्:","m":"city"},{"d":"पश्येमः","m":"will see"},{"d":"तथा:","m":"that way"},{"d":"त्वम्:","m":"you"},{"d":"कुरु:","m":"think"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"दृष्टवातांतुपुरींलङ्कांत्रिकूटशिखरेस्थिताम् ।हतंचरावणंयुद्धेदर्शनावधारय","trans":"\"If the city of Lanka situated on top of Trikuta mountain is seen, you can be sure that Ravana is killed.\"","words":[{"d":"त्रिकूटशिखरे:","m":"on top of Trikuta mountain"},{"d":"स्थिताम्:","m":"situated"},{"d":"ताम्:","m":"that"},{"d":"लङ्कांपुरीम्:","m":"city of Lanka"},{"d":"दृष्टवा:","m":"after seeing"},{"d":"युद्धे:","m":"in war"},{"d":"तु:","m":"you"},{"d":"दर्शनात्:","m":"on having a look"},{"d":"रावणम्:","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"हतम्:","m":"is killed"},{"d":"अवधारय:","m":"can determine"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"अबध्वासागरेसेतुंघोरेचतुवरुणालये ।लङ्कांनमर्दितुंशक्यासेन्द्रैरपिसुरासुरैः","trans":"\"Without building a bridge on that dreadful ocean, the abode of Varuna, it is not possible for suras or asuras accompanied by Indra also to crush Lanka.\"","words":[{"d":"घोरे:","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"वरुणालये:","m":"abode of Varuna"},{"d":"सागरे:","m":"on the ocean"},{"d":"सेतुम्:","m":"bridge"},{"d":"अबध्वा:","m":"without building"},{"d":"लङ्का:","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"सेन्द्रैः","m":"Indra"},{"d":"सुरासुरैःअपि:","m":"even suras and asuras"},{"d":"मर्दितुम्:","m":"to crush"},{"d":"नशक्या:","m":"not possible"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"सेतुर्बद्धस्समुद्रेचयावल्लङ्कास्समीपतः सर्वंतीर्णंचमेसैन्यंजितमित्युपधारय ।इमेहिसमरेवीराहरयःकामरूपिण","trans":"\"On building a bridge over the large ocean up to Lanka, when all my army of vanaras can cross over, you may consider that you have won. These vanaras are heroic in war and can assume any form at will.\"","words":[{"d":"लङ्कासमीपतः","m":"up to Lanka"},{"d":"समुद्रे:","m":"on the ocean"},{"d":"यावत्:","m":"up to"},{"d":"सेतुः","m":"bridge"},{"d":"बद्ध:","m":"on building"},{"d":"मे:","m":"mine"},{"d":"सर्वम्:","m":"all"},{"d":"सैन्यम्:","m":"army"},{"d":"तीर्णम्:","m":"crossed over"},{"d":"जितम् इति:","m":"like having won"},{"d":"उपधारय:","m":"consider"},{"d":"कामरूपिणः","m":"those who can assume any form"},{"d":"इमे:","m":"these"},{"d":"हरयः","m":"vanaras"},{"d":"समरे:","m":"in war"},{"d":"वीराः","m":"heroic"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"सेतुर्बद्धस्समुद्रेचयावल्लङ्कास्समीपतः सर्वंतीर्णंचमेसैन्यंजितमित्युपधारय ।इमेहिसमरेवीराहरयःकामरूपिण","trans":"\"On building a bridge over the large ocean up to Lanka, when all my army of vanaras can cross over, you may consider that you have won. These vanaras are heroic in war and can assume any form at will.\"","words":[{"d":"लङ्कासमीपतः","m":"up to Lanka"},{"d":"समुद्रे:","m":"on the ocean"},{"d":"यावत्:","m":"up to"},{"d":"सेतुः","m":"bridge"},{"d":"बद्ध:","m":"on building"},{"d":"मे:","m":"mine"},{"d":"सर्वम्:","m":"all"},{"d":"सैन्यम्:","m":"army"},{"d":"तीर्णम्:","m":"crossed over"},{"d":"जितम् इति:","m":"like having won"},{"d":"उपधारय:","m":"consider"},{"d":"कामरूपिणः","m":"those who can assume any form"},{"d":"इमे:","m":"these"},{"d":"हरयः","m":"vanaras"},{"d":"समरे:","m":"in war"},{"d":"वीराः","m":"heroic"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"तदलंविक्लबांबुद्धिम् राजन सर्वार्थनाशनीम् ।पुरुषस्यहिलोकेऽस्मिन् शोकश्शौर्यापकर्षणः","trans":"\"O king, therefore enough of this agitated feeling which destroys everything. In this world the valiance of man is lost if he is sorrowful.\"","words":[{"d":"राजन्:","m":"O king"},{"d":"तत्:","m":"therefore"},{"d":"सर्वार्थनाशनीम्:","m":"that which destroys everything"},{"d":"विक्लबाम्","m":"agitated"},{"d":"बुद्धिम्:","m":"feeling"},{"d":"अलम्:","m":"enough"},{"d":"अस्मिन्:","m":"in this"},{"d":"लोके:","m":"world"},{"d":"पुरुषस्य:","m":"man's"},{"d":"शोकः","m":"sorrowful"},{"d":"शौर्यापकर्षण:","m":"valiance is lost"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"यत्तुकार्यंमनुष्येणशौण्डीर्यमवलम्बता ।अस्मिन् कालेमहाप्राज्ञसत्त्वमातिष्ठतेजसा","trans":"\"Just as heroism follows a human being in this world on accomplishing a task, you who are very wise, should resort to courage and valour and rise up.\"","words":[{"d":"मनुष्येण:","m":"by a human being"},{"d":"यत्:","m":"just as"},{"d":"शैण्डीर्यम्:","m":"heroism"},{"d":"अवलम्बता:","m":"follows"},{"d":"कार्यं:","m":"task तु: you"},{"d":"महाप्राज्ञ:","m":"very wise"},{"d":"अस्मिन्:","m":"in this"},{"d":"काले:","m":"world"},{"d":"तेजसा:","m":"courage"},{"d":"सत्त्वम्:","m":"valour"},{"d":"अतिष्ट:","m":"rise up"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"शूराणांहिमनुष्या