ll see Sita crossing over the ocean that cannot be subdued.\"","words":[{"d":"वानरेषु:","m":"upon vanaras"},{"d":"समासक्तम्:","m":"entrusted"},{"d":"तेकार्यम्:","m":"this task of yours"},{"d":"नविपत्स्यते:","m":"will not be spoilt"},{"d":"अक्षयम्:","m":"that which cannot be subdued"},{"d":"सागरम्:","m":"ocean"},{"d":"तीर्त्वा:","m":"crossing over"},{"d":"अचिरात्:","m":"very soon"},{"d":"सीताम्:","m":"that Sita"},{"d":"द्रक्ष्यसे:","m":"you will see"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"तदलंशोकमालम्ब्यक्रोधमालम्बभूपते ।निश्चेष्टाःक्षत्रियामन्दास्सर्वेचण्डस्यबिभ्यति","trans":"\"O Lord of earth Enough of that pain you have experienced. Give up sorrow and take on to anger. When kshatriyas are lethargic, they become dull but all are scared at a fearful one.\"","words":[{"d":"भूपते:","m":"O Lord of earth"},{"d":"तत्:","m":"that"},{"d":"शोकम्:","m":"pain"},{"d":"आलम्ब्य:","m":"experienced"},{"d":"अलम्:","m":"enough"},{"d":"क्रोधम्:","m":"anger"},{"d":"अलम्ब:","m":"take on to"},{"d":"निश्चेष्टाः","m":"become lethargic"},{"d":"क्षत्रियाः","m":"when kshatriyas"},{"d":"मन्दाः","m":"dull people"},{"d":"चण्डस्य:","m":"at fearful one"},{"d":"सर्वे:","m":"all"},{"d":"बिभ्यति:","m":"are scared"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"लङ्घनार्थंचघोरस्यसमुद्रस्यनदींपतेः ।सहास्माभिरिहोपेतस्सूक्ष्मबुद्धिर्विचारय","trans":"\"You are endowed with subtle intellect and now think of the means to cross over this dreadful looking ocean the lord of rivers.\"","words":[{"d":"सूक्ष्मबुद्धिः","m":"one with subtle intellect"},{"d":"इह:","m":"now"},{"d":"अस्माभिःसह:","m":"along with us,उपेतः means"},{"d":"नदीपतेः","m":"lord of rivers"},{"d":"घोरस्य:","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"समुद्रस्य:","m":"of ocean"},{"d":"लङ्घनार्थम्:","m":"to cross over"},{"d":"विचारय:","m":"think of"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"लङ्घितेतस्यतैस्सैन्यंजितमित्युपधारय ।सर्वंतीर्णंचमेसैन्यंजितमित्यवधार्यताम्","trans":"\"If the vanara army can cross (the ocean) you are certain that we will conquer. Presume that the army has succeeded.\"","words":[{"d":"तैः","m":"these vanaras"},{"d":"सै